{"tid":1309832,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"Sharkoon C10 砌機","createTime":"2019-07-12T11:22:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-15T09:52:53.000Z","uid":193131,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"bb012ae95f7c167d40de4f818196ded634b10bfb","tid":1309832,"uid":193131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T11:22:20.000Z","msg":"尋日隔離post講開C10呢隻神箱，咁細的itx 箱都放到DVD drive<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁啱我部文書機換m.2 SSD要拆底板，不如直接重新砌一次呢部機，講下用atx 非模組牛，其實都可以走到線散到熱<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢隻箱最好就係4面板都可以拆出黎，砌機方便好多<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Hbp9mZY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHbp9mZY.jpg&h=b7906aa2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n因為火牛佢係set係前面，要拆前面板，拆埋個火牛架先裝到，對拖住一大堆線的非模組牛係有啲麻煩的<br />\n佢有條線帶返個火牛插頭去後面，直接將呢條線捲幾圈收靚佢就得，因為前面板會遮住佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/p7uYfmD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fp7uYfmD.jpg&h=a6c3277c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n裝好底板之後，因為火牛同側板有少少空位 就可以將條cpu 8 pin塞落去<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n初頭我想試下將呢條位收係底板下面，點知發覺煩到仆街，結果都係用返上面的方法<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DmdqEOr.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDmdqEOr.jpg&h=c7413a89&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n之後到24pin線，都係用返同一方法，塞去果條空位度，其實搞掂24pin同cpu 8pin線，非模組牛最麻煩果part已經清除左<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UgkwAoH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUgkwAoH.jpg&h=0395b9eb&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"bed5407bcaa9b5752cca725636571d4683d9abb0","tid":1309832,"uid":193131,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T11:32:33.000Z","msg":"前面板果堆線可以分開兩邊走線的<br />\n因為我塊底板front panel係右下角，所以front panel同usb 3.0我會經上面果個窿入，HD audio就下面入<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZPOeybv.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZPOeybv.jpg&h=d88a1f33&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nFront panel堆線因為太長，我塞左一part入底板下面果度，HD audio就勉強可以轉一轉彎搞掂，都係貼住側板隔離果啲空位咁走<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kiEJrxJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkiEJrxJ.jpg&h=8280bb6c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nUSB 3.0其實我覺得自己走得有啲hea，佢條線其實唔太扭得到，都係安置係火牛同另一邊側邊中間的空間<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jFYVhEG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjFYVhEG.jpg&h=528811de&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n呢一part可能對其他人未必咁有用，因為底板果啲插位會有唔同，自己調整啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n暫定，火牛其中一邊空間搞掂左24 pin同cpu 8pin，另一邊搞掂左front panel果堆線"},{"pid":"cf33b5d6b643f0c6d0f8bf03cc7c7929b23063f3","tid":1309832,"uid":46232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T11:32:33.000Z","msg":"留名學野"},{"pid":"255e99d0e3f8a15cdd5b73be945b32ad7f240901","tid":1309832,"uid":193131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T11:46:04.000Z","msg":"之後終於到重點的DVD drive<br />\n唔係為左裝佢，我點解要買c10<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n(唔係的，咁細個箱裝到240 aio都係佢屈機的地方，不過裝240 aio就裝唔到DVD drive啦)<br />\n<br />\n佢個5.25 吋架有螺絲位，可以直接將2.5 / 3.5吋 SSD / HDD裝係個底度<br />\n(其實唔咁樣裝ssd都得，反正唔驚震，就其塞佢埋一邊都得啦) <br />\n<br />\n我覺得c10最大的缺點就係，佢個2.5吋位係轉左90度，但3.5係冇事的，on撚9<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n為左呢樣野我試左唔少方法，先搵到一個收得埋啲SATA線的方法<br />\n將條SATA線轉上去機箱果個角位(前面板後面) ，再轉返落黎插SSD，再將最後一個頭插落DVD drive度<br />\n因為果個 on9轉左90度的位，你將最後一個SATA頭插SSD係會唔啱位，DVD drive上面又冇空位比我由上面轉落去<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/07/12/193937_9ee26271527d6765589f80b215254637.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F07%2F12%2F193937_9ee26271527d6765589f80b215254637.JPG&h=996ae8e2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nSATA data 線唔太麻煩，反正SSD同火牛果個空位夠多，塞哂啲線落去就得<br />\n又係因為on9 轉左90度的問題，SSD一定要用L型插頭，唔係就會頂側板<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/k4iVhJ6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fk4iVhJ6.jpg&h=be4551bc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n佢果個轉90度設計真係好on9<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"01859d6bffd1ce7773b51903011e43e5f02fd4f8","tid":1309832,"uid":193131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T11:46:52.000Z","msg":"食完飯再繼續<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a7f0d615aeb1c6fdeddb13292061a96a2978138","tid":1309832,"uid":14049,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T11:58:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3df0029698543c700242ec14207059757c85fb31","tid":1309832,"uid":113922,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T12:13:53.000Z","msg":"最勁既z390phantom拎黎做文書機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5434cb689e9c64d308d0c270765f5a692ffa6bc4","tid":1309832,"uid":138724,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T12:19:31.000Z","msg":"Lm"},{"pid":"e857e09ea6f3f8dca6ef43402a0c6e9e61712c46","tid":1309832,"uid":193131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3df0029698543c700242ec14207059757c85fb31","tid":1309832,"uid":113922,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T12:13:53.000Z","msg":"最勁既z390phantom拎黎做文書機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T12:47:29.000Z","msg":"實際用落，佢cpu超頻唔夠MSI Z370I 咁好，我真係唔明佢有幾勁"},{"pid":"4ab289d48fa576cbeb2d818afa14d24971e2e769","tid":1309832,"uid":113922,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"e857e09ea6f3f8dca6ef43402a0c6e9e61712c46","tid":1309832,"uid":193131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3df0029698543c700242ec14207059757c85fb31","tid":1309832,"uid":113922,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T12:13:53.000Z","msg":"最勁既z390phantom拎黎做文書機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T12:47:29.000Z","msg":"實際用落，佢cpu超頻唔夠MSI Z370I 咁好，我真係唔明佢有幾勁"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T12:48:58.000Z","msg":"供電最好，最多功能，ac9560，有埋tb3戰未來<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a022050d853871663c4a954a33a06f6d83832ba0","tid":1309832,"uid":193131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T12:53:10.000Z","msg":"機箱尾IO上面可以裝一隻8cm風扇，咁呢度就冇咩特別野要講的，都係典型走線方法<br />\nc10話如果唔需要加風扇，呢個位可以加一隻2.5吋SSD / HDD<br />\n不過我都係果句，SSD唔驚震駛鬼咁麻煩咩，是但啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YDapbqC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYDapbqC.jpg&h=79dacf79&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n話明係文書機，梗係唔駛裝display card直接用內顯就得啦，所以果堆冇用的線，我就咁扎埋一邊，塞左係頭先安置USB 3.0果度<br />\n不過因為機箱跟果隻風扇，係一個大4pin加一個細4pin，所以我要拉一個大4pin頭出黎駁風扇，同頭先一樣的做法，多餘線塞哂入火牛同SSD中間果個空位就得<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qs4xkkp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fqs4xkkp.jpg&h=2d4f3902&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/k56WM0q.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fk56WM0q.jpg&h=0313d8af&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b8aef137373910ceac1bd9eb377fa19c3fc97e38","tid":1309832,"uid":193131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T13:00:07.000Z","msg":"其實機就砌完啦，由頂望落去，所有線都收哂係火牛左右兩邊同側板的空位，同埋火牛同SSD中間的空位度<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n仲要機箱風扇係裝係頂蓋，我set佢就抽風，直接帶走cpu cooler的熱空氣，基本上散熱係冇問題的<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n雖然我自己懶，用stock cooler就算數，但如果其他人要換cooler<br />\n可以諗240aio(5.25吋果個位用唔到) ，120aio，或者150mm以下的塔散(呢個其實好on9，整多1cm咪可以用u12s囉，屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />) <br />\n<br />\n砌c10加埋走線，我大約用左個幾鐘就搞掂<br />\n一來我本身知大約要點砌，二來我冇display card少啲線要走，又多好多空位走線<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nMOBM0S.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnMOBM0S.jpg&h=ba56afec&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b3cd6d9160cfafaaa13ed2546e2198cba4b290da","tid":1309832,"uid":40428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T13:07:55.000Z","msg":"茶包留名學野<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39522e415c1783b7d2477f9b76a133609e206f8e","tid":1309832,"uid":16873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T14:05:11.000Z","msg":"呢個箱display card噩夢<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b180f1dd9f4e39caebf7fbd0d59c1a301c39f10","tid":1309832,"uid":193131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"39522e415c1783b7d2477f9b76a133609e206f8e","tid":1309832,"uid":16873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T14:05:11.000Z","msg":"呢個箱display card噩夢<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T14:38:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />佢都惡夢？<br />\n如果將我安置用唔著的線，同埋usb 3.0線果個位置清空<br />\n將啲線搬去5.25吋同火牛中間果個空位<br />\n(SSD求其擺，甚至唔用2.5吋，只用m.2) <br />\n長卡應該夠放的，同我拉大4pin線的方法一樣，係中間果個空位拉條6+2pin去display card"},{"pid":"b32bda2b1ddb14d673b89bfa0a3f8505c970a3fe","tid":1309832,"uid":16873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7b180f1dd9f4e39caebf7fbd0d59c1a301c39f10","tid":1309832,"uid":193131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"39522e415c1783b7d2477f9b76a133609e206f8e","tid":1309832,"uid":16873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T14:05:11.000Z","msg":"呢個箱display card噩夢<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T14:38:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />佢都惡夢？<br />\n如果將我安置用唔著的線，同埋usb 3.0線果個位置清空<br />\n將啲線搬去5.25吋同火牛中間果個空位<br />\n(SSD求其擺，甚至唔用2.5吋，只用m.2) <br />\n長卡應該夠放的，同我拉大4pin線的方法一樣，係中間果個空位拉條6+2pin去display card"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T16:09:22.000Z","msg":"厚少少已經入唔到箱<br />\n個5.25架會局限佢個插入角度"},{"pid":"a5c80c7a81cac8ff8e2d261d20d9c3ebe84a8963","tid":1309832,"uid":193131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b32bda2b1ddb14d673b89bfa0a3f8505c970a3fe","tid":1309832,"uid":16873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7b180f1dd9f4e39caebf7fbd0d59c1a301c39f10","t